        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Key Features:</h3>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">Pending Surveys:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700">
            <li>View any surveys that are assigned but not yet completed.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">Completed Surveys:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700">
            <li>Once a survey is completed, it automatically moves into this section.</li>
            <li>Students can review their previous responses at any time.</li>
            <li>If an advisor has submitted feedback, it will appear at the bottom of the survey.</li>
            <li>Surveys can be downloaded as PDFs for record-keeping.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">Notifications:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700">
            <li>Displays recent updates or reminders related to surveys and feedback.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Advisor View -->
    <section class="rounded-3xl bg-white px-8 py-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800">üßë‚Äçüè´ Advisor View</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
        The Advisor View provides tools for monitoring student progress, giving feedback, and managing student assignments.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">Student Records:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 text-slate-700">
            <li>View all students and their associated tracks.</li>
            <li>Click ‚ÄúReview‚Äù to give initial feedback on a student‚Äôs completed survey.</li>
            <li>Once feedback is submitted, the button changes to ‚ÄúEdit Feedback.‚Äù</li>
            <li>Advisors can also download surveys and feedback for documentation.</li>
            <li>Submitted feedback becomes visible to students in their Completed Surveys section.</li>
